/**
 * <p>
 * This class is a tool for migrating data from an older to a newer version
 * of an S3 filesystem.
 * </p>
 * <p>
 * All files in the filesystem are migrated by re-writing the block metadata
 * - no datafiles are touched.
 * </p>
 */
